Package PlayerWarpGUI.Commands.SubCommands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BanCommand
    Command: Add players to the ban list of a specific warp.
    DeleteWarpCommand
    Command: Delete a warp from a users warpfile
    and remove warp object from list and destory it.
    HelpCommand
    Help Command: Shows help menu to the user.
    ListCommand
    List Command:
    Show player a list of their warp they have set.
    If warp name is added then show details of that specific warp.
    SetIconCommand
    Icon Command:
    Sets the icon to show for that warp in the gui menu.
    SetLoreCommand
    SetLore Command:
    Sets the lore lines for the specified warp.
    SetTitleCommand
    SetTitle Command:
    Sets the title text shown in the gui menu for the specified warp.
    SetWarpCommand
    Setwarp Command:
    Sets a warp at the current players location for that player.
    ShowCommand
    Show Command:
    SHow the GUI menu to the player.
    UnbanCommand
    Unban Command:
    Removed player from a warps banned list for that warp and player
